name: GREEN CURRY
description: Zucchini, eggplant, green beans and basil leaves, simmered in a spicy green curry paste with coconut milk.

name: RED CURRY
description: Bell peppers, bamboo shoots, eggplant and basil leaves. This is simmered in a red curry paste with coconut milk.

name: YELLOW CURRY
description: Mild yellow curry, containing rich flavors of curry powder, coconut milk, potatoes, onions and carrots.

name: PA-NENG CURRY
description: Sweet thick paste of pa-neng curry, coconut milk, bell peppers and basil leaves.

name: MASSAMAN CURRY
description: This is a favorite Thai curry with potatoes, onions, and peanuts in coconut milk.

name: PINEAPPLE CURRY
description: Diced pineapples, bell peppers, basil leaves, in spicy Thai red curry paste.

name: JUNGLE CURRY (NO COCONUT MILK)
description: With bell peppers, green beans, squash, bamboo shoots, basil, mushrooms, baby corn, all cooked with jungle curry paste.
